# Agent Execution Policy (Persistent)

This repository follows the global rules in ~/.gemini/GEMINI.md and ~/.gemini/CLEAN_CODE.md.

Mandatory rules:
1) All page UI must be rendered by components in src/components/**.
2) Pages should not define local UI-heavy components or styling blocks.
3) UI must use src/components/ui primitives/components and approved variants.
4) Business logic must live in src/lib/**.
5) API calls must live in src/hooks/**.
6) Keep functions small, names meaningful, and avoid side-effect-heavy code.
7) Keep structure vertically separated and dense by concept.

When implementing:
- Prefer component composition over inline page JSX.
- Move API request code to hooks and pure logic utilities to lib.
- Keep page files thin and orchestration-only.
